<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css" media="screen">
      body { width: 600px; }
      .quick-links { margin-top: 50px; }
      .salutation { margin-bottom: 50px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <p class="salutation">
        Hi <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>,
      </p>
      <p>
        Congratulations! You have been hired for <%= link_to @job_application.job_posting.job.title, @job_application.job_posting.job %>, for <%= link_to @job_application.job_posting.job.organization.name, @job_application.job_posting.job.organization %>.
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>
        This is the job description for <%= @job_application.job_posting.job.title %>:
        <code>
          <%= simple_format(@job_application.job_posting.job.description) %>
        </code>
      </p>
      <p>
        You are set to be holding this position from <%= @job_application.job_posting.start_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>, to <%= @job_application.job_posting.end_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>
        Should you have any questions about the job, please send them to <%= mail_to @job_application.job_posting.job.organization.email %>. You should hear back from your supervisor in the next few days to organize your transitions into your role.
      </p>
      <p>
        Best of luck on your new job within EngSoc, and beyond!
      </p>
      <p>
        <i>Please note that all EngSoc hiring is done according to EngSoc Hiring Policy as seen in Section Gamma of the EngSoc Policy Manual available on our website under "About - Government - Governing Documents". If you have any concerns about the interview process and want to speak confidentially with someone, you can e-mail the Engineering Review Board at erb@engsoc.queensu.ca or drop a sealed envelope labeled “ERB” into the EngSoc mailbox. You will receive a response within 48 hours.</i>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-links">
      <h3>Quick links</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "EngSoc Dash", root_url %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "My Profile", profile_url(@user) %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "My Organizations", user_organizations_url %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <%= render 'shared/mail/footer' %>
  </body>
</html>
